  "time_ut": 1658550123,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dda \u0db4\u0dcf \u0db4\u0dc4\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0d86\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0d9a\u0dba\u0dcf \u0daf\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0d91\u0dc5\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd3 \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The guard was thrown out of the train and killed by the kick of the passenger",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Wayangoda police say that a railway security officer who was kicked by a train passenger threw himself out of the running train and fell down.",
        "The police also said that Shirley Lakshman Dissanayake, a 52-year-old father of two, who resided at Oruthota Road, Gampaha, Upper Yagoda, has died.",
        "Preliminary police investigations have also revealed that two persons were drinking alcohol on the inter-city train from Colombo Fort to Kankasanthure and when the railway security officers advised them not to do so, the railway security officer was kicked out of the train by one of the passengers.",
        "On a notification made by the railway ticket inspectors about two persons who were traveling on the train while drinking alcohol, when the two railway security officers were there to check them, the two persons scolded the security officers.",
        "The other railway security officer in the train informed the police that the two did not have train tickets.",
        "Police investigations have revealed that when the railway security officers tried to take the two of them from that train compartment to another train compartment, one of them kicked the railway security officer, whereupon the railway security officer was thrown out of the train door.",
        "The police also mention that the two suspects were arrested at the Mirigama railway station by a group of officers of the Mirigama police who came to know about the incident. Thus arrested",
        "The suspects have been revealed to be an army soldier and a man who is said to have worked in a train passenger canteen, the police said."
      ],
